00350 code_list_t *code_join (int n, ...)
00351 {
00352    va_list argptr;
00353    code_list_t *curlist;
00354    code_list_t *result;
00355    
00356    va_start (argptr, n);
00357    if (n <= 1)
00358       return NULL;
00359 
00360    result = curlist = va_arg (argptr, code_list_t *);
00361    if (result == NULL)
00362        return NULL;
00363 
00364    while (n - 1)
00365    {
00366       while (curlist->next != NULL)
00367          curlist = curlist->next;
00368       curlist->next = va_arg (argptr, code_list_t *);
00369       n--;
00370    }
00371    va_end (argptr);
00372    return result;
